quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim."{1},footnotes:1:1
  2,2,"This is the Book of Allah, there is no doubt in it; it is a guidance for the pious,"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  2,3,"for those who believe in the existence of that which is beyond the reach of perception, who establish Prayer and spend out of what We have provided them,"{1}{2}{3},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3
  2,4,"who believe in what has been revealed to you and what was revealed before you, and have firm faith in the Hereafter."{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  2,5,"Such are on true guidance from their Lord; such are the truly successful."